    "en": "Erdős Problem 848",
    "ja": null,
    "latex": "A set $A$ has the non-squarefree product property if $ab + 1$ is not squarefree\nfor all $a, b ∈ A$. -/\ndef NonSquarefreeProductProp (A : Finset ℕ) : Prop :=\n  ∀ a ∈ A, ∀ b ∈ A, ¬Squarefree (a * b + 1)\n\n/-- The candidate extremal set: $\\{n ∈ \\{0, \\dots, N-1\\} : n ≡ 7 (mod 25)\\}$. -/\ndef A₇ (N : ℕ) : Finset ℕ :=\n  (Finset.range N).filter (fun n => n % 25 = 7)\n\n/-- The Erdős Problem 848 statement for",
